        -> '18:07:53', 180753
@end example

@code{UTC_TIME()} is available as of MySQL 4.1.1.

@findex UTC_TIMESTAMP()
@c description_for_help_topic UTC_TIMESTAMP
@item UTC_TIMESTAMP
@itemx UTC_TIMESTAMP()
Returns the current UTC date and time as a value in @code{'YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS'}
