@item
Fixed bugs on Alpha with @code{REPLACE()} and @code{LOAD DATA INFILE}.
@item
Added @code{interactive_timeout} variable to @code{mysqld}.
@item
Changed the argument to @code{mysql_data_seek()} from @code{ulong} to
