Fixed table locks for Windows.
@item
Allow @samp{$} in identifiers.
@item
Changed name of user-specific configuration file from @file{my.cnf} to
@file{.my.cnf} (Unix only).
@item
Added @code{DATE_ADD()} and @code{DATE_SUB()} functions.
